msgid "Ws library"
msgstr "Ws library"

#: ../../source/websockets/adapter.rst:200
msgid ""
"Another available adapter is a ``WsAdapter`` which in turn acts like a "
"proxy between the framework and integrate blazing fast and thoroughly "
"tested `ws <https://github.com/websockets/ws>`__ library. This adapter is"
" fully compatible with native browser WebSockets and is far faster than "
"socket.io package. Unluckily, it has significantly fewer functionalities "
"available out-of-the-box. In some cases, you may just don’t necessarily "
"need them though."
msgstr ""

