#: ../../source/websockets/gateways.rst:2
msgid "Gateways"
msgstr "Gateways"

#: ../../source/websockets/gateways.rst:4
msgid ""
"Gateway is a class annotated with ``@WebSocketGateway()`` decorator. "
"Gateways make use of `socket.io "
"<https://github.com/socketio/socket.io>`__ package under the hood, but "
"also, provide compatibility with a wide range of other libraries, "
"including native web sockets implementation, read more `here "
"</websockets/adapter>`__."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/websockets/gateways.rst:21
msgid ""
"warning **Hint** Gateway behaves same as a simple **provider**, therefore"
" it can effortlessly inject dependencies through constructor. Also, "
"gateway can be injected by other classes (providers and controllers) as "
"well."
msgstr ""

